# Email Template Generator ‚Äî Codebase Summary

Clinical trial patient recruitment tool. Admins create campaigns, generate AI email variations, and review public copy suggestions.

## Production URLs
- Admin: `https://goodlabgroup.com/ai/apps/email-template-generator`
- Public campaign: `https://goodlabgroup.com/ai/apps/campaign/[publicId]`

## Key Config
- `basePath` and `assetPrefix` are both `/ai/apps` in `next.config.ts`
- `router.push()` does NOT need `withBasePath()` ‚Äî Next.js adds basePath automatically
- `fetch()` calls DO need `withBasePath()` ‚Äî use the helper in `campaign-builder.tsx`
- Server runs on port 3000, managed by PM2 as user `goodlabgroup`
- Node path: `/opt/nodejs/current/bin/node`

## Deploy Command
```bash
su - goodlabgroup -c "cd /home2/goodlabgroup/public_html/ai/apps/email-template-generator && git pull && /opt/nodejs/current/bin/npm ci && /opt/nodejs/current/bin/npm run build && /opt/nodejs/current/bin/pm2 restart email-template-generator && /opt/nodejs/current/bin/pm2 save"
```
After changing `.env.production`, use `pm2 restart email-template-generator --update-env`.

## Stack
- **Next.js 16** (App Router, TypeScript) ‚Äî `src/app/`
- **Supabase** ‚Äî database via `createSupabaseAdmin()` in `src/lib/supabase-admin.ts`
- **Nodemailer** ‚Äî SMTP email via `src/lib/mailer.ts`, creds in `.env.production`
- **Tailwind CSS** ‚Äî utility-first, no component library
- **OpenAI + Anthropic** ‚Äî AI generation via `src/app/email-template-generator/api/generate/`

## Database Tables
- `campaigns` ‚Äî one row per trial campaign (ingredients, metadata)
- `email_templates` ‚Äî verified templates (AI-generated or accepted submissions). All fields NOT NULL but allow empty strings `""`
- `campaign_submissions` ‚Äî pending public suggestions, `status: "pending" | "accepted" | "rejected"`

## Route Map
| Path | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `/email-template-generator` | Admin campaign library (list) |
| `/email-template-generator/[publicId]` | Admin campaign builder (edit + review queue) |
| `/campaign/[publicId]` | Public read-only page (templates + suggest copy) |
| `/email-template-generator/api/campaigns` | GET list / POST create ‚Äî has `force-dynamic` + `Cache-Control: no-store` |
| `/email-template-generator/api/campaigns/[id]` | PATCH update / DELETE |
| `/email-template-generator/api/generate` | POST AI generation |
| `/email-template-generator/api/submissions/[id]` | PATCH accept/reject ‚Üí inserts into `email_templates` |
| `/campaign/[publicId]/submissions` | POST new public submission ‚Üí triggers email notification |

## Key Components
- `campaign-builder.tsx` ‚Äî monolithic admin client component. Screens: `dashboard`, `new`, `builder`
- `campaign-tabs.tsx` ‚Äî public page tabs: Templates (AI-Generated / Verified Submissions sub-tabs), In Review, Suggest Copy
- `submission-form.tsx` ‚Äî public suggestion form: From Lines, Subject Lines, Email Body, Full Email sections

## Submission Flow
1. Public user submits via `submission-form.tsx` ‚Üí POST `/campaign/[publicId]/submissions`
2. Row inserted into `campaign_submissions` with `status: "pending"`
3. Email notification sent to `NOTIFY_EMAILS` (comma-separated in `.env.production`)
4. Admin reviews in builder ‚Üí PATCH `/email-template-generator/api/submissions/[id]`
5. On accept ‚Üí row inserted into `email_templates` with `source_type: "submission"`, missing fields set to `""`

## Display Rules
- All cards (TemplateCard, SubmissionCard) show **only populated fields** ‚Äî no "Not provided" text
- Single-field cards fill full width (no `md:grid-cols-2`)
- Body section always has a "Body" label above the pre-wrap block
- Admin `TemplateCard` shows From, Subject Line, Preview, CTA boxes ‚Äî no h2 title heading

## Email Notifications
- Sent via `src/lib/mailer.ts` using Nodemailer + cPanel SMTP (`noreply@goodlabgroup.com`)
- Recipients: `NOTIFY_EMAILS` env var, comma-separated
- Production recipients: `dan@goodlab.org, josh@goodlab.org` (+ `om@goodlab.org` for testing)
